    "client_msg_id": "c79e5819-0ad5-4f62-a7c7-53822759d11c",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Without that freedom, we're at the mercy of the ever-growing Standard to include, or not include, support for the symbols we want. I try searching the unicode space all the time for a symbol I want and come up empty (e.g. left-pointing arrows are much less numerous than right-pointing ones)",
